  "_effective_gpm_comment": "Phase 3 supply-limited scaling (PLAN.md section 3). effectiveGpm = ratedGpm * (supplyGpm / zoneRatedTotalGpm) when supplyGpm is set AND below the zone's summed rated GPM; otherwise effectiveGpm = ratedGpm. Precip rate then uses effectiveGpm in the same 96.3*gpm/area formula.",
